{"tid":377301,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"你班大學生好撚丟架啊","createTime":"2017-08-27T15:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T03:29:38.000Z","uid":17232,"like":635,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53e7e56dba6f56b2773cd948dbaa8c3c19be755c","tid":377301,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">啱啱開錯台，呢個重開</span></span><br />\n<br />\n話說小弟啱啱Ocamp玩city hunt嗰陣，我地成組人企係條街到都覺得唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n玩嗰陣組爸講依家咁多人咁憎香港既大學生，就係因為啲活動對社會好大滋擾<br />\n所以玩嗰陣都不停提我地唔好企到一舊咁塞住條街。<br />\n<br />\n佢仲提到之前有一班大學生玩ocamp嗰陣on99就咁塞住左喺間舖門口<br />\n然後個店主直情走出黎屌佢地影響舖頭生意。<br />\n<br />\n但係估唔到隔離個post 一班大學生喺大街到dem beat叫囂都可以有人狡辯話唔會滋擾到市民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家啲大學生真係痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n社會覺得你地後生仔熱血體諒唔鬧你就係人情，但係鬧你既話唔該你地就收皮。柒事唔好做比街外人睇啦，好撚丟架㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：科大freshman</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ea164d7273737423b1a85aa547059fed3d3abf1","tid":377301,"uid":119769,"like":75,"dislike":110,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75bdf11b00719b6259a233de19090b6cf0308fa5","tid":377301,"uid":125310,"like":170,"dislike":17,"score":153,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"根本玩ocamp就係丟架"},{"pid":"aff40931946696ebfafc790832f9c4a87703ee4e","tid":377301,"uid":17232,"like":149,"dislike":0,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50步笑100步<br />\n樓主我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n儘量降低滋擾，好撚過大搖大擺明知都仲要大街上面叫囂，以為自己好熱血先啦"},{"pid":"fdb9753ba86e4b7bfd5aed52daea60d0af047346","tid":377301,"uid":17232,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本玩ocamp就係丟架</blockquote><br />\n唉屌當初俾frd叫撚左去報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9ad739a9884de6ddf1630899bdfe72bf2ca4c5","tid":377301,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"負評嗰啲人講既野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652e58a52a0eff53eb6fc8abab2412a2ecba0549","tid":377301,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評嗰啲人講<span style=\"color: red;\">句</span>野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0843574e059e199bc61a9861308e4397617a678f","tid":377301,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"其實一個沙宣cheers都夠<br />\n效果仲好<br />\n唔需要出嚟銅鑼灣"},{"pid":"eab65e7fc10edf5a60b5e8fcaae0bc9435b65c11","tid":377301,"uid":140979,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"之前去銅鑼灣見到班中大生dem beat笑撚左出聲"},{"pid":"a03f9a947acc463f399250b73c7a66e73206e352","tid":377301,"uid":134936,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:06:11.000Z","msg":"有預感呢個post會有好多「大學生」負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e9ad9d34256b285e403f010a25dafa7e750d26","tid":377301,"uid":66547,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"其實呢D咪叫當局者迷囉,佢地班大學生以為自己好熱血,唔會影響到人,其實係其他人眼中呢班大學生好黑人憎"},{"pid":"93391a14711bc96fbbe4429d65a4cb212d0d7e45","tid":377301,"uid":135060,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今年都係fm玩ocamp好彩冇阻到人</span></span>"},{"pid":"f33992a7feecc52e26e30c6d5f6730b13656be6c","tid":377301,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:09:58.000Z